{"tid":1423802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【盂蘭節氣魄更壯】中聯辦路祭燒街衣大會","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:08:25.000Z","uid":193565,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5097ddc0d17399da71ad909fbf590fe719f21c23","tid":1423802,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bFgn5iV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbFgn5iV.png&h=ebc3054f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香城市民個個愛國愛港，當然要慶祝一年一度嘅盂蘭節，弘揚中華文化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而小弟覺得路祭燒街衣最佳選址就係中聯辦大樓外，根據郭嘉巴打嘅講法，路祭會引來不少孤魂野鬼，我哋路祭下捐下物資俾佢地，順手叫佢地以後係中聯辦附近盤據，之後...... 我無嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外，根據旅發局網站，盂蘭節除咗祭孤魂野鬼之外，亦係祭祖的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n郭嘉巴Post：<br />\n[靈界勢力] 一年一度嘅盂蘭節又到喇!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1397204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1397204</a><br />\n<br />\n是次路祭對象：<br />\n反送中烈士<br />\n受中共政權逼害烈士<br />\n文革、大躍進受害者<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一國兩制</span></strong><br />\n任何孤魂野鬼<br />\n<br />\nFAQs:<br />\n1. 盂蘭節燒街衣犯唔犯法？<br />\n根據支那01的新聞，香港的《空氣污染管制(露天焚燒)規例》，明文禁止多項露天焚燒活動，惟按風俗、宗教儀式、節日或慶典上，為先人、神靈獻祭而燃燒香燭冥鏹、祭品或供奉，則<span style=\"color: red;\">屬豁免之一</span>，故一般市民在盂蘭節作路祭不屬違法。<br />\n不過，如拜祭過後未有做好清理，於公眾地方遺下灰燼、香燭，市民可被食環署職員檢控。根據《公眾潔淨及防止妨擾規例》(第132BK章)， 一經定罪，最高可被判罰款2萬5千元，及監禁6個月。食環署又強調，署方亦可根據《定額罰款(公眾地方潔淨及阻礙)條例》（第570章），向亂抛垃圾的人士發出1,500元定額罰款通知書。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/225836/%E4%B8%83%E6%9C%88%E5%8D%81%E5%9B%9B%E7%9B%82%E8%98%AD%E7%AF%80-%E7%87%92%E8%A1%97%E8%A1%A3%E6%9C%83%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E7%95%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F225836%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%259B%2582%25E8%2598%25AD%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E7%2587%2592%25E8%25A1%2597%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2595%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258B%2589&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=c988f803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/225836/%E4%B8%83%E6%9C%88%E5%8D%81%E5%9B%9B%E7%9B%82%E8%98%AD%E7%AF%80-%E7%87%92%E8%A1%97%E8%A1%A3%E6%9C%83%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E7%95%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%89</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 點解中聯辦大樓係最佳選址？<br />\n中共害死咁多人，我地叫d靈界手足去搵佢地算帳都好正常姐。<br />\n<br />\n3. 驚犬會唔會唔俾？<br />\n限制宗教自由&hellip;&hellip; 我無嘢講<br />\n<br />\n簡單燒街衣教學：<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2138287/%E3%80%90%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E4%B8%83%E6%9C%88%E3%80%91%E9%AC%BC%E7%AF%80%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E7%87%92%E8%A1%97%E8%A1%A3%E6%9C%80%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%9F%E5%B8%AB%E5%82%85%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E4%B8%83%E6%9C%88%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E7%87%92%E8%A1%97%E8%A1%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2138287%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E6%259B%2586%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259C%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E7%25AF%2580%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%2587%2592%25E8%25A1%2597%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A5%25BD%25EF%25BC%259F%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2582%2585%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E6%259B%2586%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E7%2587%2592%25E8%25A1%2597%25E8%25A1%25A3&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=e7fd9d12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2138287/%E3%80%90%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E4%B8%83%E6%9C%88%E3%80%91%E9%AC%BC%E7%AF%80%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E7%87%92%E8%A1%97%E8%A1%A3%E6%9C%80%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%9F%E5%B8%AB%E5%82%85%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E4%B8%83%E6%9C%88%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E7%87%92%E8%A1%97%E8%A1%A3</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram Channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/YuLanOnline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FYuLanOnline&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=46cfcef5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/YuLanOnline</a><br />\nTelegram 討論區（可從Channel進入）：<a href=\"https://t.me/YuLanDiscussion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FYuLanDiscussion&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=b48a9389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/YuLanDiscussion</a><br />\n希望有西環街坊提供化寶盆等工具，We Connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fcf93aa1521608836c14a4c98e5a0f14419b74","tid":1423802,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"快去淘寶：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3pGO01E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3pGO01E.png&h=74ef885b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd8615c49d0b969135743a0963d9cd6f74bde112","tid":1423802,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/voRvuVb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvoRvuVb.png&h=563cc69b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nUpload錯圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d95bb8d2718d931dee165a0112020574f79aaa4","tid":1423802,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8ba130076a252becf592e5d6acc6b67a53d7549","tid":1423802,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}